item.title: On today's episode of percussive resocialization
item.description: When someone's daddy didn't beat them the way they deserved, sometimes we as society have to pick up the slack. Sometimes this behavior can go unchallenged for so long that even someone's stepson, living out MLK jrs dream, has to be the one to step up. Reinforcing socially acceptable behaviors as adults through endorsing and sanctions is known as resocialization. Sometimes resocialization can be observed being applied through percussive means. Claims that it's AI: original video dates back to 2022, AI video checking services reported back 40-58% confidence (between three services) that it may be AI, which is not a confident report. Gravity is working, ground doesn't have snakes, timing of all the subjects is organic. Edit 2: found a higher res upload from 7 years ago, also before the advent of modern AI videos, also uploaded to my page for your perusing
